    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>University of California, San Diego</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate for difference in outcome between hospital admission versus discharge after recent
      TIA, and evaluate feasibility of a larger study.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      20 patients will be randomized within 24 hours of a TIA to be admitted to the hospital or
      discharged to home, and the investigator will compare outcomes, cost, and evaluate the
      feasibility of a larger study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
